SectionBody.Text: Nothing in this act shall be construed to:

Subsection.Text: Constitute the establishment or enlargement of any rights to the use of real property or create an interest therein for the placement, construction, repair, maintenance, relocation, or excavation or demolition of any underground facility;
Waive any right of a party having an interest in real property to charge any fee for the use regarding such property; or

Preempt a governmental member operator from reasonable regulation of its right-of-way. This subsection does not exempt a municipality, county, district, or other local governmental member operator from the provisions of this chapter that apply to the member operator.
